#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:10
msgid "blockdiagの代替手段を模索したが断念した記録"
msgstr "Record of trying to find an alternative to blockdiag but giving up"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:13
msgid ""
"sphinxcontrib.blockdiagについて、Pillow 9.5 "
"依存がボトルネックだったので、諸々の移行対応を試みたが、最終的に移行を断念した記録です。"
msgstr ""
"Regarding sphinxcontrib.blockdiag, the dependency on Pillow 9.5 was a "
"bottleneck, so I tried various migration solutions, but in the end I gave up"
" on migration."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:20
msgid "背景と目的"
msgstr "Background and purpose"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:22
msgid ""
"`sphinxcontrib.blockdiag` を用いて時系列図を可視化していたサイトを管理していました。 しかし、blockdiag は "
"`Pillow 9.5` に依存しており、以降の Pillow 10.x 以降では非互換となってしまった。"
msgstr ""
"I was managing a site that used `sphinxcontrib.blockdiag` to visualize time "
"series diagrams. However, blockdiag depends on `Pillow 9.5` and is no longer"
" compatible with Pillow 10.x and later versions."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:25
msgid "`Pillow 9.5` のインストールも pip 上では終了しており、代替手段を模索する必要が生じた。"
msgstr ""
"The installation of `Pillow 9.5` was also completed on pip, so I had to look"
" for an alternative method."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:28
msgid "試したこと"
msgstr "What I tried"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:30
msgid "**Graphvizへの移行を試行**"
msgstr "**Attempt to migrate to Graphviz**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:32
msgid "blockdiag の構文を手作業で Graphviz の DOT 記法に変換。"
msgstr "Manually convert blockdiag syntax to Graphviz's DOT notation."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:33
msgid "`graphviz` ディレクティブを使って `sphinx` 上で描画。"
msgstr "Draw on `sphinx` using the `graphviz` directive."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:34
msgid "しかし、横幅・縦幅の調整に限界を感じた。"
msgstr "However, I felt there was a limit to adjusting the width and height."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:35
msgid "各ノードの大きさ指定や折返し等も Graphviz 側では厳しい。"
msgstr ""
"Specifying the size of each node, wrapping, etc. is also difficult on the "
"Graphviz side."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:37
msgid "**図の分割検討**"
msgstr "**Diagram division examination**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:39
msgid "グループ単位で図を分割し、複数の図に展開する構成を試みる。"
msgstr "Try to divide the diagram into groups and create multiple diagrams."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:40
msgid "やはり、横幅・縦幅の調整に限界を感じた。"
msgstr ""
"As expected, I felt there was a limit to adjusting the width and height."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:42
msgid "**blockdiag継続のための Pillow 9.5 固定**"
msgstr "**Fixed Pillow 9.5 for blockdiag continuation**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:44
msgid "Pillow 9.5 の公式 wheel 提供が停止されていた。"
msgstr "Official wheel provision for Pillow 9.5 has been stopped."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:45
msgid "fork による維持を試みた。"
msgstr "I tried maintaining it using fork."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:46
msgid "公式の `9.5.x` ブランチを fork。"
msgstr "Fork the official `9.5.x` branch."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:47
msgid "`setup.py` の `get_version()` を修正。"
msgstr "Fixed `get_version()` in `setup.py`."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:48
msgid "Poetry の git 依存指定でインストールには成功。"
msgstr ""
"Installation was successful with Poetry's git dependency specification."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:49
msgid "しかし、最終的に Sphinx ビルド時に `AssertionError: len(context) = 1` という深刻なエラーが発生。"
msgstr ""
"However, I ended up getting a serious error when building Sphinx: "
"`AssertionError: len(context) = 1`."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:50
msgid "他のパッケージとの依存関係の複雑さを踏まえこの手も断念。"
msgstr ""
"Given the complexity of dependencies with other packages, I gave up on this "
"option."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:53
msgid "結論"
msgstr "conclusion"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:55
msgid "blockdiag による図の可視化は、現時点では維持・移行ともに困難と判断。"
msgstr ""
"Visualizing diagrams using blockdiag is currently difficult to maintain and "
"migrate."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-02-blockdiag-migration-failure.rst:56
msgid "該当ページの管理をいったん **中断** し、代替の可視化方法やツールが整備されるまで凍結する。"
msgstr ""
"Temporarily **suspend** the management of the relevant page and freeze it "
"until alternative visualization methods and tools are in place."

